    "In 1866 Murray attracted the attention of <a href=\"/ruskinj\">John Ruskin</a> who arranged for additional training as an assistant to the Pre-Raphaelite painter Edward Burne-Jones.": [],
    "Murray also painted for William Morris and copied paintings for Rossetti.": [],
